    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-preserved condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior, reflects a standard of care synonymous with a collector-grade asset. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated enthusiast to acquire a truly peerless example.",
